<BaseLayout title="Breeders & Rescues in New Jersey">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">New Jersey Breeders & Rescues</h2>
  <p class="mb-4">Discover reputable breeders and rescue organizations for exotic pets. Always research thoroughly and prioritize adoption when possible.</p>
  <ul class="mb-4">
    <li class="mb-2">
      <strong>Jersey Exotics Rescue</strong><br/>
      Based in Newark, NJ<br/>
      Specializes in small mammals and reptiles.
    </li>
    <li class="mb-2">
      <strong>Garden State Breeders</strong><br/>
      Located in Trenton, NJ<br/>
      Offers captive-bred reptiles.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p>Know of an organization we missed? <a href="/contact" class="text-primary font-bold underline">Contact us</a> to share details.</p>
</BaseLayout>